情就应该这样。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fans-complain-of-fainting-long-queues-and-overheating-outside-yungbluds-first-bludfest-2024-3782961">粉丝抱怨 Yungblud 首届 Bludfest 2024 外晕倒、排长队和过热的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
