/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Denzel-Curry@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Denzel-Curry@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在退出最近的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/korn">KoRn</a>节目后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denzel-curry">丹泽尔·库里</a>向粉丝们承诺，他将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">雷丁和利兹大学</a>向他们“弥补”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/denzel-curry-cover-interview-2022-melt-my-eyez-see-your-future-3268998">丹泽尔·库里：“当今最伟大的说唱歌手？谁能告诉我我不是？”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位另类说唱明星将于昨晚（8 月 11 日）为新金属传奇人物 KoRn 表演，当时他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-korn-play-biggest-uk-show-to-date-at-gunnersbury-park-footage-setlist-3782868">正前往 Gunnersbury Park 参加他们迄今为止在英国规模最大的演出</a>。</p><p>库里原定在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/loathe">Loathe</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wargasm">Wargasm</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">Spiritbox</a>的早期表演后登上舞台，但在最后一刻宣布他因失声而被迫退出活动。</p><p>据最新消息称，他曾考虑过是否要坚持参加西伦敦的比赛，但最终决定反对，因为他不想“冒着进一步受伤的风险”或表现平淡。他还确保那些失望的人会得到解决，因为他计划在 2024 年的雷丁和利兹举办的活动中注入活力。</p><p> “我向伦敦所有的粉丝道歉，但由于失声，我今晚无法表演，”他在 Instagram 故事中开始发表声明。</p><p> “我想每个人都知道我在表演时有多疯狂，但连续的表演对我造成了伤害，我不想冒进一步受伤的风险或进行一场半途而废的表演……我会成功的由雷丁大学和利兹大学的你们决定……我保证。大超” </p><figure id="attachment_3782937" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3782937" style="width: 1650px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3782937" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/denzel-curry-screenshot@2000.jpg" alt="丹泽尔·库里 Instagram 故事的屏幕截图" width="1650" height="2929" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/denzel-curry-screenshot@2000.jpg 1650w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/denzel-curry-screenshot@2000-400x710.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/denzel-curry-screenshot@2000-800x1420.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/denzel-curry-screenshot@2000-696x1236.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/denzel-curry-screenshot@2000-1392x2471.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/denzel-curry-screenshot@2000-1068x1896.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1650px) 100vw, 1650px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3782937" class="wp-caption-text">丹泽尔·库里的 Instagram 故事的屏幕截图。图片来源：@denzelcurryph/Instagram</figcaption></figure><p>昨晚的演出是 KoRn 在 1 月份宣布的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/korn-announce-huge-summer-2024-uk-shows-in-london-scarborough-and-halifax-buy-tickets-3567091">2024 年英国夏季三场大型演出中</a>的最后一场——继斯卡伯勒和哈利法克斯的演出之后。这也标志着他们七年来在首都的首次演出。</p><p>诸如“Got The Life”、“Y&#39;All Want A Single”、“Blind”和“Falling Away From Me”等热门歌曲出现在 16 首歌曲的曲目列表中，然后他们以最热门的歌曲“Freak On A”结束了当晚的演出。皮带”。</p><p> 《Coming Undone》和《Shoots And Ladders》也进行了现场演奏，并根据现场表演进行了改编，乐队在前者中融入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">Queen</a>的《We Will Rock You》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a>的《One》的简短演绎在后者中。查看下面的演出片段和歌单。</p><p>今年在 Gunnersbury Park 系列演出的还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-grennan-announces-biggest-ever-headline-show-at-london-gunnersbury-park-buy-tickets-3492259">Tom Grennan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/peggy-gou-announces-massive-summer-headline-show-at-londons-gunnersbury-park-3589644">Peggy Gou</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fisher">FISHER</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pj-harvey">PJ Harvey</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3782941" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3782941" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3782941" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Denzel-Curry-live@2000x1270.jpg" alt="丹泽尔·库里在舞台上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Denzel-Curry-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Denzel-Curry-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, http