loads/2024/08/Yungblud-Lil-Yachty@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Yungblud-Lil-Yachty@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Yungblud-Lil-Yachty@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Yungblud-Lil-Yachty@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yungblud">Yungblud</a>首次在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-announces-second-stage-line-up-for-bludfest-buy-tickets-3761400">BLUDFEST</a>演出，并邀请<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-yachty">Lil Yachty</a>作为惊喜嘉宾。查看下面的片段和完整的歌单。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-interview-bludfest-festival-milton-keynes-new-album-buy-tickets-3602830">Yungblud 向我们讲述他的过去、现在、未来和新音乐节 BludFest</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周末（8 月 11 日）在米尔顿凯恩斯的国家碗举行，该活动标志着新音乐节的首次举办，也是这位歌手职业生涯迄今为止最盛大的演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-play">Soft Play</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nessa-barrett">Nessa Barrett</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-damned">The Damned</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/LOLA-YOUNG">Lola Young</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jazmin-bean">Jazmin Bean</a> 、Noahfinnce、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jesse-jo-stark">Jesse Jo Stark</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/landon-barker-on-dad-travis-musical-feedback-he-doesnt-let-me-down-easy-3546593">Landon Barker</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a>鼓手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-barker">Travis Barker</a>的儿子）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hannah-grae">Hannah Grae</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aziya">Aziya</a>等也参与了演出。</p><p>在他的演出中，Yungblud（真名多米尼克·哈里森）以连续演唱《Superdeadfriends》、《我爱你，你愿意嫁给我吗？》、《葬礼》和《加州》开场，然后爆发了各种粉丝最受欢迎的歌曲包括《Breakdown》、《Parents》和《Lowlife》。</p><p>然而，这场演出的一大亮点是 17 首歌曲的歌单中有 12 首歌曲，歌手让 Lil Yachty 演绎了他们的联合歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-lil-yachty-when-we-die-can-we-still-get-high-3577419">“When We Die (Can We Still Get High?)”，</a>令粉丝们大吃一惊。这首歌是哈里森 2024 年的第一首单曲，自 2019 年以来一直与这位说唱歌手合作。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="yungblud 亮相 2024 年 bludfest 米尔顿凯恩斯碗 | yungblud残疾人观景台。" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/R0aGMrGYzh4?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>演出期间的其他精彩时刻包括 Yungblud 表演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-yungbluds-defiant-new-single-fleabag-3024641">《Fleabag》</a> ，并邀请三名幸运粉丝与他一起上台为这首 2021 年歌曲弹吉他。</p><p>随后，他还翻唱了 2019 年的歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-machine-gun-kelly-yungblud-travis-barkers-collab-think-im-okay-2505576">“I Think I&#39;m OKAY”</a> ，这是他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/machine-gun-kelly">Machine Gun Kelly</a>和 Travis Barker 合作发行的歌曲。查看更多演出片段、粉丝反应以及下面的完整演出列表。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C-kHecRo4g7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div>